snippet.title: "Kagamine Rin / Len Happy 14th Birthday" downloadable content is now available!
snippet.description:
The new stages have "Kagamine Rin / Len Happy 14th Birthday"  themed eggs, birds, and berries!
Collect exclusive berries in new stages to find special birds and birds with limited items!
Exclusive egg designs and special events for this stage... !?

■Title: Hatsune Miku Connecting Puzzle TAMAGOTORI
■Release date: January 27th, 2022 (Thursday)
■Genre: Puzzle
■Supported hardware: Nintendo Switch
■Number of players: 1
■Suggested retail price: 1,500 yen
　"Kagamine Rin / Len Happy 14th Birthday" Downloadable Content: 500 yen
■Purchasing method: Nintendo eShop (download-only software)
■Twitter：https://twitter.com/cfm_mobile
